spec_data.Name: terminator
spec_data.Description:
Multiple GNOME terminals in one window.  This is a project to produce
an efficient way of filling a large area of screen space with
terminals. This is done by splitting the window into a resizeable
grid of terminals. As such, you can  produce a very flexible
arrangements of terminals for different tasks.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 09:14:39 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Store and run multiple GNOME terminals in one window
